```

The following patterns are _not_ considered problems:

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
a { background: url('x.jpg'); }
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
@import url("foo.css");
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
@font-face { font-family: "foo"; src: url("foo.ttf"); }
```

### `"never"`

Urls _must never_ be quoted.

The following patterns are considered problems:

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
a { background: url('x.jpg'); }
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
@import url("foo.css");
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
@font-face { font-family: "foo"; src: url('foo.ttf'); }
```

The following patterns are _not_ considered problems:

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
a { background: url(x.jpg); }
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
@import url(foo.css);
```

<!-- prettier-ignore -->
```css
